	Rounded {1 setlinejoin 1 setlinecap} if} def
/AL {stroke userlinewidth 2 div setlinewidth
	Rounded {1 setlinejoin 1 setlinecap} if} def
/UL {dup gnulinewidth mul /userlinewidth exch def
