	0 -4 M 12 8 L stroke}
>> matrix makepattern
/Pat5 exch def
<< Tile8x8
 /PaintProc {0.5 setlinewidth pop -2 8 M 4 -4 L
	0 12 M 8 -4 L 4 12 M 10 0 L stroke}
>> matrix makepattern
/Pat6 exch def
